### ============================================
### 4.5 INSIGHT IA ENDPOINT
### ============================================

### POST /v1/insight/generate
### Generar explicación IA para respuesta incorrecta
POST {{baseUrl}}/insight/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attemptId": "{{attemptId}}"
}

### ============================================
### ERROR CASES
### ============================================

### POST /v1/insight/generate - Attempt not found
POST {{baseUrl}}/insight/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attemptId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### ============================================

### POST /v1/insight/generate - Invalid UUID
POST {{baseUrl}}/insight/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attemptId": "not-a-uuid"
}

### ============================================

### POST /v1/insight/generate - Without auth
POST {{baseUrl}}/insight/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attemptId": "{{attemptId}}"
}

### ============================================
